“The test aircraft did not stay on the ground longer than planned,” Beaudoin said during a conference call, adding that ground tests and software updates were planned during the plane’s downtime.
Each manufacturer plans differently.
We decided to make a first flight and have an update period, and that's what we did.
This will occur throughout the flight program.
